flowchart TD
    %% Smart Context Routing via MASTER_INDEX.md — matches actual trigger groups

    START([Session Start]) --> IDX[Read MASTER_INDEX.md<br/>memory router]
    IDX --> ALWAYS[Load Always group<br/>core-policies.md]

    ALWAYS --> MATCH{Match task vs<br/>trigger keywords}

    MATCH -->|setup, bootstrap,<br/>command, lifecycle| CONFIG["Load Config group<br/>(harness-config.md)"]:::group
    MATCH -->|architecture, pattern,<br/>stack, domain, adr| KNOW["Load Knowledge group<br/>granular: PKB, ADR log,<br/>architecture, glossary,<br/>tech-stack, constraints"]:::group
    MATCH -->|security, auth,<br/>simplicity, ponytail| RULES["Load Rules group<br/>granular: security.md,<br/>ponytail.md,<br/>code-design.md"]:::group
    MATCH -->|heuristic, lesson,<br/>recurring, we always| LEARN["Load Learned group<br/>(learned-heuristics.md)"]:::group
    MATCH -->|domain triggers<br/>via glossary.md frontmatter| DOMAIN["Load Domain Pack<br/>granular per file:<br/>glossary → boundaries<br/>patterns → anti-patterns"]:::group
    MATCH -->|debug, failure,<br/>regression, retro| DEBUG["Load Debug group<br/>(harness-telemetry.md +<br/>prior session-extracts.md)"]:::group
    MATCH -->|no trigger matches| SKIP["Skip intent groups<br/>(Always group only)"]:::group

    CONFIG --> FEAT
    KNOW --> FEAT
    RULES --> FEAT
    LEARN --> FEAT
    DOMAIN --> FEAT
    DEBUG --> FEAT
    SKIP --> FEAT

    FEAT["Load Feature Artifacts<br/>(status.md, spec.md, plan.md,<br/>tasks.md, handoff.md,<br/>testing-scenarios.md)"]:::group

    FEAT --> PHASE[Apply Phase × Guidance Matrix<br/>trim files no longer needed<br/>for current delivery phase]
    PHASE --> REPORT[Report Context Loaded<br/>+ reasons for skips]:::group
    REPORT --> WORK([Begin work])

    STALE[MASTER_INDEX.md missing<br/>or stale] -.->|fallback| ALL[Load every memory file<br/>route gap to context-memory]:::fallback
    IDX -.->|if missing| STALE

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef router fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff
    classDef group fill:#eef2ff,stroke:#c7d2fe,color:#3730a3
    classDef decision fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef fallback fill:#fcf3f3,stroke:#f2c4c4,color:#c62828

    class START,WORK terminal
    class IDX,ALWAYS router
    class CONFIG,KNOW,RULES,LEARN,DOMAIN,DEBUG,SKIP,FEAT,REPORT group
    class MATCH decision
    class STALE,ALL fallback
